	"description": "It was almost like a dream. I had taken 6 months off to go all in on coding and\nmoving to Australia with my girlfriend, when I finally returned to Norway — and\na job.\n\nIt almost went without a hitch. I had it all. I’ll start by providing you a bit\nof my entrepreneurial background.\n\nI spent the last 6 months tirelessly working on my portfolio and personal\nprojects. Most notably, I created CryptoDasher [https://cryptodasher.com/], a\ntool for tracking Crypto currencies and portfolio values in real ",
