	"description": "6 September 2017\nSweat is running down my face. I’m staring down a blank sublime text document.\nWhat on earth am I doing? My hands are resting above the keyboard of my MacBook\npro.\n\nThere is enough friction to cuddle each of the keyboard buttons my fingers are\nresting on.\n\nIt’s like apologizing to them for not using them yet.\n\nIt’s late at night, and I’ve decided to jump in head first, creating my own app\nusing React and Firebase.\n\nHow, I don’t know.\n\nI only know that I’m going to do it, no matt",
